Project-Perabird
================

About
-----

Project Perabird is what will become a MMORPG game...
Perabird is released under the terms of the GNU General Public License, see COPYING for more information.

Credits go to:
 * Zeg9 for code
 * jmf for ideas and textures


Compiling
---------

To compile project perabird, you will need:
* CMake >= 2.6
* OpenGL
* GLEW
* SDL 1.2.*
* SDL_image
* AGuiSy (latest version: https://github.com/Zeg9/aguisy)

To start compiling, type the following commands:
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ..
  make
Then you can start by typing:
  ./perabird


Troubleshooting
---------------

Please report any problem at this URL:
  https://github.com/Zeg9/project-perabird/issues

